{"tid":608034,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同個仔去藥房 佢見到一盒嘢問我...","createTime":"2018-03-27T21:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T01:42:12.000Z","uid":73202,"like":1,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"91dad8884d1082a5095fd58842feb942bebe1bb2","tid":608034,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:44:23.000Z","msg":"我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傻仔:daddy 呢盒咩嚟㗎？<br />\n我:呢盒咪係condom囉傻仔<br />\n<br />\n傻仔:condom係用嚟做咩㗎？<br />\n我:發生性行為嗰陣用㗎<br />\n<br />\n傻仔行埋去拎起咗盒3個裝嘅condom:點解呢個係3個嘅<br />\n我:3個裝係for中學生用嘅 星期五，六，日 每日用一個<br />\n<br />\n傻仔又拎起咗個6盒裝問:咁呢個呢？<br />\n我:for大學生嘅 星期五，六，日 每日用兩個！<br />\n<br />\n傻仔又行埋去拎起個12盒裝..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681d2fb5ee3111fca0117e36fa43a743dea63c17","tid":608034,"uid":134376,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EV4fnQHe-5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEV4fnQHe-5Y&d=3FUI6DqlVR5Qxu5qoE%2FXcNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=21301e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EV4fnQHe-5Y</a><br />\n好有創意喎樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4980fa60d5113ec133cb49d73a8a428713dfe67c","tid":608034,"uid":42212,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"681d2fb5ee3111fca0117e36fa43a743dea63c17","tid":608034,"uid":134376,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EV4fnQ